Chordate/Smokescreen/Ramhorn:


Chordate sighed.  "Alright, Kluster." he said into his com, there's someone 
to see you."

Smokescreen stopped at the shield, seeing Battera and Chordate.  "Who are 
you?" he directed the question to the female.

===

Ramhorn went into stasis lock, his chest plate barely hanging on.
